ghost-role-information-rules-team-antagonist = 
    You are a [color=vermelho][bold]Antagonista da equipe[/bold][/color]. Suas intenções são claras e prejudiciais à estação e à sua tripulação.
    You must [bold]work with your team[/bold] or follow reasonable directions from your team leaders.
    You don't remember any of your previous life, and you don't remember anything you learned as a ghost.
    You are allowed to remember knowledge about the game in general, such as how to cook, how to use objects, etc.
    You are absolutely [color=red]NOT[/color] tem permissão para lembrar, digamos, o nome, aparência, etc. do seu personagem anterior.
